# Infinity-War

### Overview

There are six kind of infinity stones with random numbers every time the game starts. When the user clicks on the infinity stone it adds the number. To win the game you must get the total of the given number.

## Infinity War Game

![Header](assets/images/readme/game.png)

1. This is a guessing game using numbers where the player will guess with numbers.

2. There will be six infinity stones displayed as buttons on the page.

3. The user will be shown a random number at the start of the game.

4. When the user clicks on an infinity stone it will add a specific amount of points to the user's total score.

5. The user wins the game if their total score matches the random number. Alternatively, the user loses the game if their total score goes above the random number.

6. The amount of points each infinity stone adds is not shown to the user, but their total score is displayed and updated after each infinity stone is clicked.

7. The number of games won and lost will be displayed.

8. If the user successfully matches their total score to the random number they get 1 win, if the user's total score is above the random number the user get 1 loss, either way the game restarts.

9. When the game is restarted, the user will be shown a new random number, all the crystals will now have 4 different hidden values, and the user's total score is reset to 0.

